{
  "stem": "1765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were carrying things on their backs, you see, and they dropped them as the loads got too heavy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he pretended that he was crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he walked and walked and walked, for days and days and days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He walked nights, and he hid during the days in the woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at one point, he fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a tank-- a German tank-- was just a few feet away from him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it moved, and he was saved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You see, you never know how people are saved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A few feet of space between a man's head and a tank, and the man is dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Eventually, he made his way to a town called Czestochowa, which is spelled, I guess, in the English, Czestochowa, C-H-E-S-T-O-C-H-O-W-A.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Czestochowa, where he had business associates from before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Along the way, he stopped at the-- he had some money, which he took out of his uniform, and put it in his underwear.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had some money, and he bought pants that were too short and a greasy shirt from this farmer who let him sleep in-- in the barn as he was running.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Running-- he was escaping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was going into the German territory, rather than east.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was going west because he felt that-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he knew people in a town which was fairly close within actual walking, and walking, and walking distance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came to these people's house, and introduced himself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't believe him, because he didn't look like Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Samuel Rudominski, from Vilna, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he reminded them of things that they bought, and they did together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they hid him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans were already there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
